[
    {
        "text": "So, when is a form of speech considered a dialect versus a language?",
        "startTime": 313,
        "endTime": 4102,
        "slowStartTime": 620,
        "slowEndTime": 6378
    },
    {
        "text": "It seems reasonable that the degree of mutual intelligibility...",
        "startTime": 4443,
        "endTime": 8011,
        "slowStartTime": 6814,
        "slowEndTime": 12242
    },
    {
        "text": "...would determine whether two ways of speaking...",
        "startTime": 8261,
        "endTime": 10379,
        "slowStartTime": 12541,
        "slowEndTime": 15794
    },
    {
        "text": "...are classified as separate languages or as dialects of the same language.",
        "startTime": 10503,
        "endTime": 14511,
        "slowStartTime": 15905,
        "slowEndTime": 21991
    },
    {
        "text": "But as we've seen, there are many occasions where this is not the case.",
        "startTime": 14858,
        "endTime": 18165,
        "slowStartTime": 22437,
        "slowEndTime": 27472
    },
    {
        "text": "Perhaps surprisingly, the distinction between a language and a dialect...",
        "startTime": 18595,
        "endTime": 22212,
        "slowStartTime": 28043,
        "slowEndTime": 33543
    },
    {
        "text": "...usually has nothing to do with pronunciation, vocabulary,...",
        "startTime": 22411,
        "endTime": 26199,
        "slowStartTime": 33766,
        "slowEndTime": 39524
    },
    {
        "text": "...or any other linguistic features.",
        "startTime": 26330,
        "endTime": 28231,
        "slowStartTime": 39645,
        "slowEndTime": 42571
    },
    {
        "text": "However, it's not coincidental, either.",
        "startTime": 28583,
        "endTime": 31009,
        "slowStartTime": 43024,
        "slowEndTime": 46739
    },
    {
        "text": "It's a matter of politics.",
        "startTime": 31346,
        "endTime": 32733,
        "slowStartTime": 47169,
        "slowEndTime": 49324
    },
    {
        "text": "The basis for what's officially deemed a language...",
        "startTime": 33539,
        "endTime": 36265,
        "slowStartTime": 50458,
        "slowEndTime": 54622
    },
    {
        "text": "...was shaped by the emergence of a European nation states beginning around the 1500s.",
        "startTime": 36339,
        "endTime": 41036,
        "slowStartTime": 54658,
        "slowEndTime": 61779
    },
    {
        "text": "In order to establish and maintain centralized governments,...",
        "startTime": 41414,
        "endTime": 44587,
        "slowStartTime": 62271,
        "slowEndTime": 67105
    },
    {
        "text": "...clear territorial boundaries, and state-sponsored education systems,...",
        "startTime": 44933,
        "endTime": 48928,
        "slowStartTime": 67550,
        "slowEndTime": 73617
    },
    {
        "text": "...many nation states promoted a standardized language.",
        "startTime": 49202,
        "endTime": 52205,
        "slowStartTime": 73953,
        "slowEndTime": 78533
    },
    {
        "text": "Which form of speech was chosen to be the standard language...",
        "startTime": 52637,
        "endTime": 55619,
        "slowStartTime": 79106,
        "slowEndTime": 83653
    },
    {
        "text": "...was usually based on what people spoke in the capital.",
        "startTime": 55823,
        "endTime": 58555,
        "slowStartTime": 83884,
        "slowEndTime": 88058
    },
    {
        "text": "And while other forms of speech persisted, they were often treated as inferior.",
        "startTime": 59041,
        "endTime": 63357,
        "slowStartTime": 88712,
        "slowEndTime": 95260
    },
    {
        "text": "This tradition extended across the globe with European colonization...",
        "startTime": 64047,
        "endTime": 67897,
        "slowStartTime": 96220,
        "slowEndTime": 102071
    },
    {
        "text": "...and into modern times.",
        "startTime": 68162,
        "endTime": 69536,
        "slowStartTime": 102393,
        "slowEndTime": 104529
    },
    {
        "text": "Italy, for example, has at least 15 of what might be called regional dialects.",
        "startTime": 70002,
        "endTime": 74844,
        "slowStartTime": 105153,
        "slowEndTime": 112491
    },
    {
        "text": "One of them, the Florentine dialect,...",
        "startTime": 75170,
        "endTime": 77288,
        "slowStartTime": 112905,
        "slowEndTime": 116157
    },
    {
        "text": "...became known as Standard Italian when the country politically unified in 1861.",
        "startTime": 77519,
        "endTime": 83104,
        "slowStartTime": 116429,
        "slowEndTime": 124881
    },
    {
        "text": "It was selected because legendary authors like Dante and Machiavelli...",
        "startTime": 83502,
        "endTime": 87508,
        "slowStartTime": 125403,
        "slowEndTime": 131487
    },
    {
        "text": "...used it in their original works.",
        "startTime": 87757,
        "endTime": 89544,
        "slowStartTime": 131786,
        "slowEndTime": 134541
    },
    {
        "text": "And it came to represent an image of Italian national identity...",
        "startTime": 89763,
        "endTime": 93613,
        "slowStartTime": 134794,
        "slowEndTime": 140645
    },
    {
        "text": "...that some found particularly desirable.",
        "startTime": 93897,
        "endTime": 96155,
        "slowStartTime": 140995,
        "slowEndTime": 144457
    },
    {
        "text": "Later on, in his attempt to establish a unified, fascist state,...",
        "startTime": 96499,
        "endTime": 100645,
        "slowStartTime": 144898,
        "slowEndTime": 151193
    },
    {
        "text": "...Italian dictator Benito Mussolini saw language standardization...",
        "startTime": 100838,
        "endTime": 105123,
        "slowStartTime": 151407,
        "slowEndTime": 157909
    },
    {
        "text": "...as an important objective.",
        "startTime": 105421,
        "endTime": 106919,
        "slowStartTime": 158282,
        "slowEndTime": 160604
    },
    {
        "text": "His government promoted standard Italian...",
        "startTime": 107395,
        "endTime": 109353,
        "slowStartTime": 161243,
        "slowEndTime": 164254
    },
    {
        "text": "...while prohibiting other forms of speech from the public sphere,...",
        "startTime": 109530,
        "endTime": 112452,
        "slowStartTime": 164445,
        "slowEndTime": 168903
    },
    {
        "text": "...framing them as backward and unsophisticated.",
        "startTime": 112798,
        "endTime": 115967,
        "slowStartTime": 169347,
        "slowEndTime": 174176
    }
]